): conform code-opencode shared split references (recursive)\n1922cffed7 docs(sk-code): conform code-opencode rust split references (recursive)\n3d79317657 docs(sk-code): conform code-opencode js/shell/typescript split references (recursive)\n6279a16bc1 docs(sk-code): conform code-opencode config/python single-file references + js direct\n2d24db2619 docs(sk-code): conform code-quality checklist assets to create-skill template\n885f2ca5c5 refactor(hooks): remove checked-in Superset/Copilot hook bridge\n3c9be4f16e docs(sk-code): restyle catalog content paths\n9e240dea14 fix(sk-code): remediate deep-review findings, add review artifacts (018)\ncfaf1fc701 docs(sk-code): split code-quality checklist + record code-review exemptions (018/011)\n4fc8ffa52b fix(sk-code): repair blank-line drops + relative-link depth in reference splits (018/007-010)\n65076fe5c8 docs(sk-code): split code-webflow other references into topic parts (018/010)\n9f81477f4b docs(sk-code): split code-webflow implementation references into topic parts (018/009)\na063d1a652 docs(sk-code): split code-opencode non-Rust + shared references into topic parts (018/008)\n640e1fc265 docs(sk-code): split code-opencode Rust references into topic parts (018/007)\na1adf95345 feat(sk-code): register Rust across 5 sk-code-local touchpoints (018 phase 005, partial)\n14f64ad89b docs(sk-code): author Rust standard docs for code-opencode (018 phase 002)\nb2f6c3ee52 feat(sk-doc): execute the category-folder de-numbering migration\nc425653a1e chore(repo): publish spec-metadata sweep, archive reorg, and close-out docs\n","exit":0,"truncated":false},"title":"git status --short && git log --all --oneline --decorate -25 -- '.opencode/specs/sk-code/019-split-doc-template-alignment' '.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-opencode/references' '.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-opencode/assets' '.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-webflow/references' '.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-webflow/assets' '.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-quality/assets'","time":{"start":1783912467614,"end":1783912467615}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_09bbfd2e8cf10090016a5458131a5481918f6ca649176d32df"}},"id":"prt_f59780b1a001X2Hk2mfVEGMhWj","sessionID":"ses_0a68bc60effeJzWL51JC6bkniv","messageID":"msg_f59777c8b001R4striWjqU0bS1"}}
